features: Pack of 3 Baby Bottles: Feed your baby in style with our fun Disney-inspired infant bottles; the convenience and flexibility of feeding your newborn is even better with this cute Winnie The Pooh baby bottle set of 3.

Durable and Safe Materials: The durable plastic materials are tested for safety and free from harmful substances; the flip-lid that covers the baby bottle prevents a mess before and after feedings but is easy to open.

Large 9 Ounce Size: Our large 5 oz baby bottles are ideal for infants 4 months and older but can also be used for newborns 0-3 months old who only eat a few ounces and quickly move to eating more as they grow.

Gifts for Baby Showers: Give our baby bottle set of 3 as a baby shower gift or as a Christmas present to new parents; consider cleaning these baby bottles with our Disney bottle brushes or gently wash on the top shelf of your dishwasher.
body.description: Feed your baby with these adorable blue baby bottles featuring Disney Characters. These 5 oz baby bottles are made from BPA-free materials and checked for safety. The extra wide nipple is medium flow and works for infants of all ages. Newborns only need a few ounces at first but quickly gain more of an appetite, so the 5-ounce capacity of this baby bottle is convenient The color is a soothing and calming color for a baby bottle and gender neutral enough that this bottle works for baby girls and baby boys. Gift this baby bottle set to new parents during Christmas, baby showers, and other special occasions.
